    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 15th level you and your comrades have formed a close bond with one another.</p><p> When you and your party roll for initative, or you enter your Slayer's Quarry state, you and all allies gain a number of temporary hit points and temporary chakra points equal to 3 times the number of allies present in battle with you.</p><p> These temporary resources stack with other sources of temporary resources of the same type.</p><p> You can benefit from this feature 3 times per long rest.</p><p></p>",
